Rebel Wilson, 42, and her beau Ramona Agruma, 38, look smitten with each other in new photographs shared during their romantic trip to Italy. The Australian actress posted a series of snaps to her 11.2 million Instagram followers which included the couple partying with friends and enjoying a stroll through the picturesque holiday destination.Rebel and Ramona looked lovely in maxi dresses.Rebel sported a blue, white and red number with a straw hat while Ramona opted for a white ensemble. 